name: Acrobat (Münzenloher Software)
overview: Not to be confused with the Acrobat game that was published in COMPUTE! magazine, this is a little known game, and a clone of Clowns/Circus for the Atari 8-bit computers. Little is known of the game other than the fact it was developed and released by a company called Münzenloher Software. The year of release it not known.
